Package dev.javafp.util

Class ImMaybe<T>

java.lang.Object
dev.javafp.val.ImValuesImpl
dev.javafp.util.ImMaybe<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
HasTextBox, Values, Serializable
public class ImMaybe<T> extends ImValuesImpl

A wrapper around a value that might be missing.

You can test if there is a value using isPresent().

If you try to get the value from a ImMaybe and it is missing, it will throw an exception.
